modules.description: This module handles WebSocket client and server communication using the Async concurrency library, managing message framing and protocol handshake. It works with `Async.Reader`/`Writer`, `Pipe.Reader`/`Writer`, and `Frame.t` for sending and receiving WebSocket messages. Use it to implement real-time bidirectional communication, such as chat servers or live data feeds, by upgrading HTTP connections or directly handling WebSocket frames.
